-- KKR Reports Co-CEO Kravis Received $70.5 Million Total Compensation in '09
-- Bill Koenig
-- 2010-07-06T14:29:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-06/kkr-reports-co-ceo-kravis-received-70-5-million-total-compensation-in-09.html

          
          
             KKR & Co. said Co-Chief Executive
Henry Kravis received total compensation of $70.5 million last
year while Co-CEO George Roberts received total compensation of
$70.5 million during the same period.  
 The information was disclosed in a regulatory filing.  
          
          


  


        